dc_description_s: This data layer represents addresses for Green Lake County, Wisconsin in 2012. Points are located at the access (center of driveway at edge of highway pavement), not on the structures. GLA plaques around Big Green Lake are numbers for the Green Lake Association.
uw_supplemental_s: This is an archived copy of the data held at UW-Madison. For the most current data available, please visit: https://hub-greenlakecowi.hub.arcgis.com/pages/opendata
